	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=39551><span id=Guru>Osano</span></a><br><b><span id=Guru>Guru</span></b><br><span id=notbold>171 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [3.95]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>While buying my usual four stacks of bandages the other day, I started wondering how much PP I would have in the bank if I had *never* bought bandages.&nbsp;&nbsp;At a bit over 1PP/stack ... maybe 1 stack per 2 blue exp lines on average, given that I tend to solo a lot (very choosy about groupmates) ... hmmmmmmm, that's a lotta PP.  Not that bandages are optional, unless you *really* like sitting on your butt waiting for Mend to refresh.<br><br>I shoulda made friends with more magicians and hit them up for summoned bandages at the beginning of each session ... heh heh.<br><br>Speaking of magicians ... here's a fun thing:  Ask one to summon you a ring of levitation ... has 2 charges.  Now, when you're goofing off somewhere (like EC tunnel), lev yourself and practice FD -- talk about Dead Man Floating.  Looks hilarious, and always gets humorous comments, people stopping to look, and a lot of questions about the floating corpse.</p>&nbsp;<br>Osano<br>Level 44 Human Monk<br>Tholuxe-Paells</td></td></tr>
