	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=634><span id=Scholar>Altizar</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>104 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [2.95]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>You need money, Kurn's tower is great for making money, you'll need to be in your mid teens before you can start raking it in, but all you have to do is collect bone chips, I mean lots of them, I gathered a bag of about 160 chips, 8 full stacks, and then took a little trip to OverThere (go through warslik woods) and do this /auction WTS 8 stacks of bonechips.&nbsp;&nbsp;Sit back and let the offers just roll in.  I sold my bag for 200pp.  Trust me High Level Necros have a lot of more important things (at least they think they do) to do than spend the 2-3 days neccessary to gather that many chips.</p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
